OL,7,FWords by ITV News Producer, Kieran
OL,8,FCarter
OL,10,FIt has been reported that guidance
OL,11,Ffrom the Equalities and Human Rights
OL,12,FCommission (EHRC) on how businesses
OL,13,Fshould provide and handle single sex
OL,14,Fspaces could be delayed for as much as
OL,15,Fa year.
OL,17,FThis comes after the EHRC urged the
OL,18,Fgovernment to speed up its
OL,19,Fpublication, with a draft text being
OL,20,Fsubmitted to Equalities Minister
OL,21,FBridget Phillipson over two months ago.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
