OL,7,FThe Times suggested the guidance's
OL,8,Fpublication could now be delayed
OL,9,Ffurther whilst the government seek
OL,10,Ffurther assessment on how much
OL,11,Fcomplying with the new guidance's
OL,12,Frecommendations could cost businesses.
OL,14,FPushing back on this, a government
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: "We have always
OL,16,Fbeen clear that the proper process
OL,17,Fneeds to be followed, which includes
OL,18,Funderstanding the potential impact on
OL,19,Fbusinesses, public functions and
OL,20,Fservices."
