OL,7,FThe updated guidance seeks to clarify
OL,8,Fthe law for organistions in the wake
OL,9,Fof April's Supreme Court ruling on the
OL,10,Flegal definition of a "woman" for the
OL,11,Fpurposes of single sex spaces.
OL,13,FMany businesses and organisations have
OL,14,Freported waiting for its publication
OL,15,Fin parliament before implementing any
OL,16,Fchanges.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
