OL,7,FThe EHRC had earlier this month warned
OL,8,Fthe government that the failure to
OL,9,Fpublish updated guidance meant some
OL,10,Fbusinesses were inadvertently
OL,11,Foperating illegally in the wake of the
OL,12,FApril's Supreme Court ruling.
OL,14,FSpeaking Friday morning, Downing
OL,15,FStreet welcomed the "clarity" it said
OL,16,Fthe Supreme Court had brought to the
OL,17,Fdefinition of "women".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
