OL,7,FA government spokesperson went on to
OL,8,Fconfirm: "The EHRC has submitted a
OL,9,Fdraft Code of Practice to ministers,
OL,10,Fand we are working at pace to review
OL,11,Fit with the care it deserves.
OL,13,F"This is a 300-page-long and legally
OL,14,Fcomplex document, and it is important
OL,15,Ffor service providers that we get this
OL,16,Fright."
