OL,7,FResponding to the government's failure
OL,8,Fto publish the guidance it submitted,
OL,9,Fthe EHRC insisted it sought to clarify
OL,10,Fthe law for businesses, but did not
OL,11,Fchange the legal situation as it
OL,12,Fcurrently stood.
OL,14,F"We do not think it necessary for the
OL,15,FEHRC to assess the cost to businesses
OL,16,Fof complying with the law, ahead of
OL,17,Four updated services Code of Practice
OL,18,Fbeing laid in parliament," an EHRC
OL,19,Fspokesperson told ITV News.
