OL,7,F"The Code is not regulation, nor is it
OL,8,Flegislation. It is practical guidance
OL,9,Fto help duty bearers understand what
OL,10,Fthe law requires of them and how they
OL,11,Fcan comply with it.
OL,13,F"These obligations are imposed by the
OL,14,FEquality Act 2010, not by the guidance
OL,15,Fwe provide on it. The law is in place
OL,16,Fand duty bearers should be ensuring
OL,17,Fthat they comply with it now.
