OL,7,FIn a letter from the outgoing chair of
OL,8,Fthe EHRC, published in The Guardian on
OL,9,FTuesday, Baroness Falkner sought to
OL,10,Freassure businesses the updated advice
OL,11,Fhad not been rushed and would help
OL,12,F"balance the rights of service users"
OL,13,Falongside those at risk of
OL,14,Fdiscrimination.
OL,16,F"I must also emphasise that it is the
OL,17,FEquality Act that businesses need to
OL,18,Fimplement. It is the law they must
OL,19,Fcomply with," wrote Falkner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
