OL,7,F"Fairness and equality benefit all of
OL,8,Fus. Implementing the law may have some
OL,9,Funwelcome costs, but contesting
OL,10,Flitigation through tribunals and
OL,11,Fcourts will have different financial
OL,12,Fand reputational costs too."
OL,14,FShe concluded: "As a regulator, we do
OL,15,Fnot make the law. We advise on it and
OL,16,Fuphold it."
