OL,7,FThe lack of guidance comes as a new
OL,8,Freport published by trans rights
OL,9,Fgroup, TransActual, suggested four out
OL,10,Fof five trans people now avoid single
OL,11,Fsex spaces in public altogether.
OL,13,FThe report took responses from around
OL,14,F430 individuals who claimed to have
OL,15,Falready been severely impacted by the
OL,16,FSupreme Court's ruling in 2025.
OL,18,FAmong the trans people who submitted
OL,19,Ftheir experiences, four out of five
OL,20,Fadmitted adapting their lives to avoid
OL,21,Fsingle-sex spaces in public altogether.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
