OL,7,FThe report also found that those with
OL,8,Fdisabilities or long-term conditions,
OL,9,Fand those visibly gender non-
OL,10,Fconforming, had higher rates of
OL,11,Fchallenge or refusal of access to
OL,12,Fcertain spaces.
OL,14,FOne cisgender woman who responded
OL,15,Fdescribed how people questioning her
OL,16,Fgender in bathrooms had become more
OL,17,Faggressive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
