OL,7,F"Before the ruling, any challenges had
OL,8,Fbeen gentle, like 'oh by the way this
OL,9,Fis the ladies' and people were
OL,10,Fembarrassed or apologetic when I said
OL,11,F'it's okay, I'm a girl.' But now it's
OL,12,Faggressive and horrible."
OL,14,FOne trans man also described feeling
OL,15,F"ashamed" when confronted in a toilet
OL,16,Fafter the Supreme Court ruling.
